[b]Shops:

Add this to your shops.cfg replace the shop number with whatever you want and add whatever you want in the shop.[/b]

[code=java]shop = 22	Dung_Exchange	2	2[/code]

[b]Action handler:
Make the shop open when clicked.[/b]

[code=java]case NPC_ID:
this.c.getShops().openShop(22);
break;[/code]

[b]Item:

Your making this item stackable.[/b]

[code=java]itemStackable[4278] = true;[/code]

